summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 66E, Page 160 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located in Block 2, Columbia Heights and in Block 2, Hillman City Addition to The City of Seattle, Division No. 1 from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone and General Commercial (CG) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of John P. Rader, et al.; C.F. 289393).
